page_description_1_part_1:
This website generates a liveablity index
                score that ranks the suburbs based on your responses to the
                questionnaire you just finished.
page_description_1_part_2:
To find out more about liveability, see
                our page 'What is Liveability'
page_description_2:
The suburbs that are your best match (i.e.
                highest liveability score) are in dark green. Those with the
                lowest are dark pink.
page_heading: Here are the Melbourne suburbs that we think are suitable for you
